Combine Shreddies, cranberries, and pecans in a large bowl. Microwave chips and oil in medium microwaveable bowl on MEDIUM 2 min., or until mostly melted, stirring once. Stir until all chocolate is melted and smooth. Stir in orange rind. Pour over Shreddies mixture while stirring to combine. Transfer mixture to parchment paper lined 9-inch square pan. Cool and chill 1 hour before breaking apart into clusters.